divs: Sighting DetailsSighting Report: I saw a total of four lights, 2 on top were blinking and two on the bottom were white. It wasn t a plane because they moved differently. It was fast and moved all over the sky. Its March 19 2005. It was about 8:30ish when I saw it. I was walking home from a friends. It was a clear sky, very freaky.
